data.description: Up to $5000. of buyers closing costs will be paid by the seller. Meticulously Remodeled four-bedroom home. Upon entering you will be greeted by a wood fireplace, vaulted ceiling living room. You will love the designer kitchen with high end finishes. The home has wood look long plank gray ceramic tiles throughout. Outside, the property offers a spacious yard perfect for hosting outdoor parties or creating your own outdoor oasis. The Garage, new roof and recently upgraded AC system check off all of your home needs. Do you want a turnkey property? This home is for you!
